WEBVTT

00:00.051 --> 00:01.522
Come on!

00:05.384 --> 00:07.634
Really? So why French?

00:10.087 --> 00:12.259
You are still with us, Wilkinson?

00:12.330 --> 00:15.246
Well, I couldn't leave without
giving him a whipping first.

00:15.994 --> 00:17.356
- Ah!
- Yes!

00:17.357 --> 00:18.802
You were saying?

00:22.803 --> 00:24.968
- Oh dear.
- Yeah.

00:25.175 --> 00:27.843
Tension's still there.
I don't want to lose him.

00:28.519 --> 00:31.638
- And Costante, it's his sister?
- Yeah.

00:31.915 --> 00:33.473
No leads.

00:34.626 --> 00:36.850
This was a good idea
to have us for a drink.

00:36.851 --> 00:38.126
It's a good team.

00:38.127 --> 00:40.024
- Come on!
- I don't want it to break up.

00:40.065 --> 00:42.904
Teams like this stay together, despite, and

00:43.106 --> 00:45.684
sometimes because of adversity.

00:46.948 --> 00:50.579
_

00:51.183 --> 00:52.589
Can you turn this up, please?

00:52.590 --> 00:55.051
... players of both sides,
were filing down the tunnel,

00:55.067 --> 00:57.653
shortly after Legia's
victory this afternoon,

00:57.670 --> 00:59.426
when the explosion happened.

00:59.600 --> 01:02.778
The source of the blast
is, at this stage, unclear.

01:02.820 --> 01:06.533
But it's believed to have originated
from the home changing room.

01:06.550 --> 01:09.203
This is what we have from moments before.

01:09.704 --> 01:12.722
Fredi, how difficult has it been
to keep your mind on the football,

01:12.742 --> 01:14.441
with all the abuse you've received?

01:14.449 --> 01:15.768
It's been tough,

01:15.908 --> 01:17.266
I'm not gonna lie.

01:17.392 --> 01:19.315
We just keep playing our game, and

01:19.316 --> 01:22.232
hope people will see beyond
the color of our skin.

01:22.233 --> 01:24.954
Well, your all-action display
in mid-field would've hurt.

01:24.955 --> 01:27.349
Congratulations, you've
been named man of the match.

01:27.433 --> 01:30.706
Thank you, but I cannot accept
this. It's gotta go to my teammate.

01:30.733 --> 01:32.480
This is the real star here.

01:34.787 --> 01:36.917
Uh, one more question,
please. One more question.

01:37.037 --> 01:40.045
Er, do you feel Legia has turned
a corner with this recent victory?

01:40.089 --> 01:41.393
Yeah, yeah, I do.

01:41.513 --> 01:43.373
Uh, things are gonna be different now.

01:43.493 --> 01:45.913
- We're going up.
- Well, thank you and good luck.

01:45.932 --> 01:49.662
Well, Fredi and the team have played
like absolute champions today, and I...

01:53.067 --> 01:57.058
_

01:57.059 --> 02:03.381
_

02:03.382 --> 02:05.210
The bomb went off in their locker room.

02:05.240 --> 02:07.039
Manager and one player dead,

02:07.045 --> 02:10.541
six players injured, one... very seriously.

02:10.542 --> 02:13.423
Kalifa Konare, he lost
his leg above the knee.

02:13.770 --> 02:16.561
The local police are claiming are
claiming international terrorism,

02:16.562 --> 02:18.999
- which is where we fit in.
- Has anyone claimed it?

02:19.006 --> 02:20.878
- No.
- Police could be trying to deflect

02:20.879 --> 02:22.913
attention from the far-right element.

02:23.172 --> 02:25.638
Black players are abused
in grounds all over Europe.

02:25.639 --> 02:27.591
So, it might be racially motivated?

02:27.606 --> 02:29.096
Legia Lubin was recently bought

02:29.097 --> 02:31.730
by a Malaysian businessman,
named Victor Arshad.

02:31.735 --> 02:35.225
Foreign ownership of football
clubs in Poland is very unusual.

02:35.226 --> 02:38.079
And the fan base isn't
exactly crazy about the idea.

02:38.080 --> 02:39.397
Demonstrations,

02:39.398 --> 02:41.729
boycotts, the ultras have also been known

02:41.730 --> 02:45.105
to send death threats to both
Kalifa Konare and Fredi Diagho.

02:45.106 --> 02:47.039
They're recent signings from Mali.

02:47.040 --> 02:48.240
What are ultras?

02:48.361 --> 02:49.827
Hooligan fans,

02:49.836 --> 02:51.887
most of them are far-right activists.

02:51.888 --> 02:54.282
They look like a very nice group of people.

02:54.451 --> 02:57.868
These players from Mali are seen
as a symbol of Arshad's ownership.

02:57.894 --> 02:59.632
What do we know about the device?

02:59.663 --> 03:01.805
Luke and I are heading
down to talk to forensics,

03:01.817 --> 03:04.338
Marco and Arabela, head to the hospital.

03:04.339 --> 03:05.691
Let's figure this out.

